fields.title: Test: Beef Stew
fields.excerpt: A traditional braised beef casserole with thick, rich gravy and chunky veg – an ideal recipe for cheap cuts, as slow-cooking guarantees a tender dish.
fields.instructions:
Chop the beef into cubes

slice the onion

Dice the potatoes & carrots

Add water and all ingredients into oven safe bowl

Bake for 1 hr £ 180 degrees
